message:
Initial commit

Starting fresh after cleanup and also there were some API keys in old repo
Added gatsby-plugin-catch-links plugin, "composes" links now uses <Link> instead of <a>.
Added basic pagination using gatsby-paginate. Fixes #4.
Added Zeit now deploy scripts to package.json

Move code snippets to markdown (#93)

* Add prismjs for highlighting

* Update post template for in-markdown code

* Move code snippets from frontmatter to markdown

* Update theme for code snippets

replace prismjs with gatsby-remark-vscode

* Update frontmatter fields set

* Update code snippets theme

* Update mdx language property
Add Typescript types definition for all hooks
